 sociology, philosophy, psychology, and health promotion and medicine.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mai 2023) 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Gerontology.2bisacsh1 aMoody, Harry R., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPhillips, Judith, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBristol University Press Complete eBook-Package 2015z97831111964280 cprintz978184742559140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781847426024423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781847426024/original  a978-3-11-119642-8  Bristol University Press Complete eBook-Package 2015b2015  aGBV-deGruyter-alles